&lt;li&gt;Identify, qualify, and advance pipeline across Navy commands, program offices, and associated systems integrators and prime contractors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track Navy IT modernization initiatives, budget cycles, and acquisition strategies to anticipate and shape opportunities ahead of the competition.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
